      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;I am pretty sure he took most of that into account. The problem I think raid warriors face inparticualr is that they have to go high hp compared to AC on the bases of you can only mitagate so much. Don't get me wrong AC is really nice and I am not trying to through out the benefits at all, but&amp;nbsp;as mobss start hitting harder the need to the hp so you&amp;nbsp;can have enough of a hp pool for a heal to land. I don't think translate well to group environment where the extra hp buffer isn't as needed and AC gets some good value back.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
